# Coffee_Machine

## Overview
This repository contains a Python-based coffee machine application that simulates the functionality of a coffee machine, allowing users to make various types of coffee. 
The application is built using object-oriented programming principles, with custom classes and functions.

## Features
- Create different types of coffee (e.g., espresso, latte, cappuccino).
- Customize the amount of coffee beans, milk, and water for each coffee.
- Check the available resources (coffee beans, milk, water) in the machine.
- Refill the resources as needed.
- Track the money earned from coffee sales.
- Allow users to place orders and calculate change.
